ComicInfo.Summary:
Adventure to an Alternate Universe!: Rick and Morty travel to an alternate world where their respective roles as mad genius and reluctant helper are reversed... and wish they hadn't.
E.T. Clone Home: While Jerry is out golfing, the large crawling insect-like alien creature, that he clumsily and unknowingly released, creates evil clones of Morty and Beth. Summer comes home and fights off the clones of her brother and mother until Rick, who has escaped from the Clackspire Labyrinth prison, shows up to obliterate the creature and the Morty clone, stunning Summer in the process. Jerry comes home from his day of golf, whistling a happy tune, only to find the aftermath of the clone battle.
